title: Ministry of Sound - Gotta Have House Music All Night Long (2014)

Ministry of Sound - Gotta Have House Music All Night Long (2014) 

            House, Club, Funky, Tech | Ministry of Sound Recordings

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 03:57:26 | 618 Mb


We kick off with the epic UK No.1 Single, "I Wanna Feel" from Second City, before moving into a fusion of classic anthems from Kings of Tomorrow, Maurice, Pete Heller and George Morel amongst modern day smashes from Ben Pearce, MK, Klangkarussell and Tensnake. Mix 2 starts with the legendary "Your Love" from the godfather of house, Frankie Knuckles.
